# Implementation Plan: Integrate Registration into Index.html

## Goal Description

Integrate full registration functionality directly into the existing signup form in [index.html](file:///c:/xampp2/htdocs/uplodedFile/index.html) (lines 2872-2937), eliminating the need for the separate [register.html](file:///c:/xampp2/htdocs/uplodedFile/register.html) page. The signup form already exists but needs password strength validation, proper field IDs, and integration with the existing [api/register.php](file:///c:/xampp2/htdocs/uplodedFile/api/register.php) backend.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **No breaking changes** - This only enhances the existing signup form without affecting the login functionality.

